1. Get source code of Hunspell from
	http://hunspell.sourceforge.net/

2. Build hunspell library
2.1. Currently only i386 works, see
	http://sourceforge.net/tracker/index.php?func=detail&aid=1740138&group_id=143754&atid=756395
for the details of this issue.

2.2. Under the source code folder:
	> ./configure && make && sudo make install

3. Come back here and do:
	> make

4. Put hunspell dictionary files to the proper place:
4.1. Get affix and dictionary files from
	http://ftp.services.openoffice.org/pub/OpenOffice.org/contrib/dictionaries/en_US.zip

4.2. Unzip en_US.zip here.

4.3. Do it here:
	> sudo make install
